---
import {Icon} from 'astro-icon'
import {
  AnnouncementBar,
	Button,
	CustomerQuoteSection,
	ThreeColumnTextSection,
	YouTubeEmbedSection,
  StickyTextImageSection,
  CtaCardSection
} from '@littlesticks/odyssey-theme-components';
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro';
import TextAndImageHero from '../components/sections/heros/TextAndImageHero.astro';

const seo = {
	title: 'Popstar Photo Booths | Lead Generation',
	description: 'Turn your events into a lead generating machine.',
};
---

<Layout seo={seo} >
	<CtaCardSection>
		<h2>Lead Generation Overview</h2>
		<p>This guide outlines the core features of our lead generation funnel. It takes you through the user journey from when they first interact with the "Tap to Start" screen all the way to collecting data and remarketing. Each step along the way is an opporunity to showcase your brand and messaging, ultimately leading to data capture and new warm leads.</p>
	  </CtaCardSection>
	<TextAndImageHero reversed>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>Tap to Start Screen</h1>
			<p>The first thing attendees see and interact with is the "Tap to Start" screen. With our lead gen package, we customize this with your messaging and branding to maximize awareness for your business.</p>
		</div>
		<picture slot="image-container">
			<img
				src="/assets/images/home/music.png"
				alt="Astro Odyssee"
				id="home-hero-image"
			/>
		</picture>
	</TextAndImageHero>
	<TextAndImageHero reversed>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>Custom Photo Frame</h1>
			<p>After an attendee takes a picture(s), they are presented with their photos in a custom photo frame. We include your branding, logos, messaging to elevate and spread your brand.</p>
		</div>
		<picture slot="image-container">
			<img
				src="/assets/images/home/photo-frame.jpg"
				alt="Astro Odyssee"
				id="home-hero-image"
			/>
		</picture>
	</TextAndImageHero>
	<TextAndImageHero reversed>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>Call to Action</h1>
			<p>After an attendee views their photo, they have the option to text or email it to themselves. The text or email they receive will have their photo and a section that we customize with your CTA, branding and any other information you would like to add.</p>
		</div>
		<picture slot="image-container">
			<img
				src="/assets/images/home/email.png"
				alt="Astro Odyssee"
				id="home-hero-image"
			/>
		</picture>
	</TextAndImageHero>
	<TextAndImageHero reversed>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>Image View</h1>
			<p>After an attendee opens their email, they will click a link to download their photo. The photo landing page has a section that we customize for your business.</p>
		</div>
		<picture slot="image-container">
			<img
				src="/assets/images/home/image-view.png"
				alt="Astro Odyssee"
				id="home-hero-image"
			/>
		</picture>
	</TextAndImageHero>
	<TextAndImageHero reversed>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>Gallery View</h1>
			<p>When an attendee clicks to view the gallery for the whole event, they will see a "Presented by: Your business name" as well as a CTA with a link of your choosing.</p>
		</div>
		<picture slot="image-container">
			<img
				src="/assets/images/home/gallery-view.png"
				alt="Astro Odyssee"
				id="home-hero-image"
			/>
		</picture>
	</TextAndImageHero>
	<TextAndImageHero reversed>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>Remarketing</h1>
			<p>This is the best part. After your event you will receive all of the phone numbers and email collected at our booth. You can then set up a remarketing email / text campaign to nurture your audience.</p>
		</div>
		<picture slot="image-container">
			<img
				src="/assets/images/home/remarketing.png"
				alt="Astro Odyssee"
				id="home-hero-image"
			/>
		</picture>
	</TextAndImageHero>

	<CtaCardSection>
		<h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
		<p>Let's do it!</p>
		<Button href="/contact" customIcon>
		  Contact Us
		  <Fragment slot="icon">
			<Icon name="ic:baseline-chevron-right" />
		  </Fragment>
		</Button>
	  </CtaCardSection>

</Layout>

<style>
#home-hero-image {
  max-height: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  width: 100%;
}

</style>